Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.00,0:24:08.38,hg3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(640,670)}あまつかぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.46,0:24:13.13,hg3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灰飛通天途
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.46,0:24:13.13,hg3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(640,670)}くものかよひぢ ふきとぢよ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.09,0:24:15.72,hg3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但使留天女
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.09,0:24:15.72,hg3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(640,670)}をとめのすがた
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.51,0:24:18.39,hg3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,片刻人間顧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.51,0:24:18.39,hg3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(640,670)}しばしとどめむ
